span => used to provide style to an part of the text., An inline element.
div=> used to define a section in an html document., An block element.
e.g => 
span{
font-size:28px;
color:lightgreen;
}
div{
color:orange;
}
<div>
<p>This is <span>HTML and CSS</span></p>
</div>

NOTE: span tag takes the precedence over div tag hence the color for the text HTML and CSS will come as lightgreen only.
